#. Max bytes: 41
msgctxt "Offset_0x2E0_Len_41"
msgid "Kiryu-san... Thank you so much for today."
msgstr "Kiryu-san... Grazie mille per oggi."

#. Max bytes: 55
msgctxt "Offset_0x460_Len_55"
msgid "It made me really happy when you said\nwe were together."
msgstr "Mi ha reso felice sentirti dire\nche stavamo insieme."

#. Max bytes: 73
msgctxt "Offset_0x600_Len_73"
msgid "That was the first time someone I've loved\nhas ever said that about me..."
msgstr "È la prima volta che qualcuno che amo\ndice questo di me..."

#. Max bytes: 25
msgctxt "Offset_0x7C0_Len_25"
msgid "My heart is still racing."
msgstr "Ho ancora il batticuore."

#. Max bytes: 66
msgctxt "Offset_0x930_Len_66"
msgid "The only one who was able to see the\nreal me... was you all along."
msgstr "L'unico a vedere la mia vera natura... sei sempre stato tu."

#. Max bytes: 48
msgctxt "Offset_0xAD0_Len_48"
msgid "Kiryu-san... I'm going to be brave today,\nand..."
msgstr "Kiryu-san... Oggi sarò coraggiosa\ne..."

#. Max bytes: 26
msgctxt "Offset_0xD00_Len_26"
msgid "This is so embarrassing..."
msgstr "Che imbarazzo..."

#. Max bytes: 50
msgctxt "Offset_0xE70_Len_50"
msgid "I would like it if you'd...\nkeep on protecting me."
msgstr "Vorrei che tu...\ncontinuassi a proteggermi."

